<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Processes other than fire primarily disturb stands. Because of the harsh, open environment and the seasonal nature of herbs, fire is unlikely unless non-native plants invade sites in successive wet years and provide fine fuels to carry fire.</div>
